[{"id":796476,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1628872948","description":"<ol>\n<li>早高峰，相同时间段，相同线路，预计时间严重不准。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>高德预计：40 分钟，但实际 1 小时 20 分钟。\n实际每天差不多，（下雨天时间更长），\n但是高德地图还是显示 40 分钟。\n结果，开出去表小时后，高德显示还要 40 分钟。</p>\n<p>它就不能学习调整一下吗？</p>\n<ol>\n<li>非高峰时间，车子开的快飞起，也没法在预计时间内到达。\n是不是高德把红灯时间都默认绿灯了？</li>\n</ol>\n<p>感觉高德预计时间少报一点，就能用户代认为你导航更智能些？</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>看样子我要试试其他导航，\n看有没有导航这方面时间预测准的？</p>\n<p>之前用过几次百度地图，但是语音听着不太习惯，也对百度这家公司不喜欢。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796476","replies":116,"created_ts":1629253383,"created":"10:23:03","title":"吐槽一下高德地图导航，能不能走点心啊","author":"zealinux","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zealinux","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/97cec5ffbda3f47b2cd453cf10b78244?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796627,"node":"MacBook Pro","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1615111860","description":"两款都有 刘海！<br />明年的 MBA 也有同款刘海<br />你们还想要吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796627","replies":111,"created_ts":1629292071,"created":"21:07:51","title":"关于新款 MBP。。","author":"ty98","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ty98","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b94347959d73d3718141bdc2072af793?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796557,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533","description":"<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/001NO9rDgy1gtkttq5uudj60ch0m8taf02.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> ","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796557","replies":110,"created_ts":1629271194,"created":"15:19:54","title":"别说什么自己做的更健康，为什么不努力让自己每顿都吃的起健康的大餐？","author":"luoyelusheng","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/luoyelusheng","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b771854cbf1c154a4fd80432d7877d4b?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796529,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533","description":"<p>买的雷柏 mt750l,无论是 2.4 还是蓝牙都能感觉到明显的发飘,想问问有没有用 g502 无线版的哥们,鼠标会发飘吗</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796529","replies":90,"created_ts":1629264414,"created":"13:26:54","title":"无线鼠标发飘是通病吗","author":"smy14520","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/smy14520","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3f78bc078d049a41d40d2ced1fb2d9c2?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796552,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1628872948","description":"<p>服务器和数据密码都是写在代码的配置文件里的，开发人员离职需要重新修改一遍，比较麻烦，有没有比较好的解决方案不需要修改？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796552","replies":67,"created_ts":1629270319,"created":"15:05:19","title":"关于开发人员离职 服务器和数据库密码修改问题","author":"followyourheart","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/followyourheart","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/61ca/ba6d/180100_mini.png?m=1519452293"},{"id":796457,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1628872948","description":"<p>肯定不能手拿着看吧，肯定得放桌子上，但是放桌子上的时候，由于书比较厚，还得用手压着看，我看淘宝上有卖那种读书支架的，不知道怎么样。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796457","replies":66,"created_ts":1629250831,"created":"09:40:31","title":"怎么能用更舒服的方式看比较厚的实体书？","author":"zhoudaiyu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhoudaiyu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b75f/9ee0/163414_mini.png?m=1574570790"},{"id":796466,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1607656854","description":"<p>Mac 上常用 swish 这个软件\n然后就想去买了个正版\n美区节点打开官网，啊 16 刀算下来 100 多块钱呢\n我怎么记得 hk 节点只要 79 港币\n一看 果然港区只要 79 港币算下来只要 65 块钱左右\n就赶紧刷了 paypal 买了感觉自己赚到了\n然后买完了突然想到印度节点打开会不会有惊喜\n于是我打开一看 299 印度卢比\n我怀着忐忑的心去查了一下汇率，算下来只需要 26 块钱左右……后悔</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796466","replies":62,"created_ts":1629252173,"created":"10:02:53","title":"感觉自己是正版软件受害者","author":"pphu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/pphu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0163/1aac/302640_mini.png?m=1629251045"},{"id":796439,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1628873021","description":"<p>在一家外包公司干了半年，很不爽，想离职，但这样的没有离职补偿。我就开始每天按时打卡下班，客户分配的任务基本延期，本来安排就不合理，要你天天加班才能完成。客户一开始只在每周例会说我，后来投诉到项目经理那，项目经理找我谈话，就问我是不是最近干的不开心，也没说扣绩效，辞退的事。难道我混的还不够吗，要怎么才能混到公司容不下我。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796439","replies":60,"created_ts":1629244948,"created":"08:02:28","title":"怎么才能让公司把你辞退","author":"VHacker1989","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/VHacker1989","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e1f3aa28bbb7691f787ac5e3d539599d?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796569,"node":"MacBook Pro","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1615111860","description":"<p>以前想的是笔记本屏幕越大越好，但是觉得通勤的话 还是轻点的好\n之前通勤是神舟笔记本 10 多斤的 所以感觉就算 16 存也不会多重\n各位彦祖们呢，</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796569","replies":51,"created_ts":1629273196,"created":"15:53:16","title":"如果新的 macbook 出来了 ，大家是买 14 寸的还是买 16 寸的呢","author":"shilianmlxg","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shilianmlxg","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/05ba/0783/363963_mini.png?m=1619767243"},{"id":796544,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533","description":"<p>搜索了下 发短信给(833) 672-1001 查 ip 没回复的。是什么原因，还有其他办法吗</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796544","replies":49,"created_ts":1629268584,"created":"14:36:24","title":"google voice 如何保持正常使用？","author":"razios","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/razios","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/23bf25ca6d4df60efc393c6b2cf5fb50?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796607,"node":"知乎","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/zhihu","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b789/2fb3/937_mini.png?m=1584298330","description":"如果一个人，比如我，每天只刷 b 站，知乎，v2ex，youtube<br />那么跟只刷微博（不是鄙视微博，只是不喜欢看娱乐新闻）的人似乎没有本质区别，只是活在一个内容不一样的茧房，但是它仍然是个茧房，信息的来源完全不由你自己控制，被算法以及背后的人工支配<br /><br />明智的选择是像一条蠕动的毛毛虫那样：自己造一个茧房<br />利用 rsshub 作为信息来源，收集全网的高效信息，搭配好用的 rss 阅读器，同时向 rsshub 贡献它没有的源<br />可以做到完全支配自己的信息世界","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796607","replies":45,"created_ts":1629281096,"created":"18:04:56","title":"如何突破信息茧房？","author":"mightofcode","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mightofcode","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/70fa/e20b/190743_mini.png?m=1624001187"},{"id":796585,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1626622970","description":"<p>很早之前 TapTap 就是要存储权限，但是不给的话也能去 Android/data/com.taptap 下面把安装包找出来</p>\n<p>但是现在强更后的版本将安装包下载到了 /data/data/com.taptap 下</p>\n<p>也就是说不 root 手机的情况下只能老老实实给存储权限</p>\n<p>平台自己都如此做,对里面游戏的审核力度现在也保持怀疑了</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796585","replies":39,"created_ts":1629276563,"created":"16:49:23","title":"TapTap 最近强制更新后不给存储权限无法安装游戏","author":"xmt328","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xmt328","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ee0586bf5a7bb1b50b23f136c9f7c083?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796474,"node":"MacBook Pro","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1615111860","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796474","replies":39,"created_ts":1629253302,"created":"10:21:42","title":"买 M1 MBP 还是等 M1X MBP？","author":"DarinJi","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/DarinJi","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9dc4/9951/175182_mini.png?m=1591437641"},{"id":796523,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533","description":"<p>目前已有 kindle oasis，不过看 pdf 体验太差，再考虑买一个平板，不知道到底该买安卓的平板还是 iPad ？用过的给点使用体验。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796523","replies":37,"created_ts":1629261668,"created":"12:41:08","title":"用 iPad 看 pdf 或其他电子书体验如何","author":"jdhao","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jdhao","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f308/ebec/316281_mini.png?m=1544159242"},{"id":796531,"node":"DevOps","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/devops","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3871/bd64/622_mini.png?m=1625081807","description":"首先说说，目前的处于离职状态，有房贷一个月 4500 左右 离职原因：被上家单位压榨太严重想休息休息，还有一个原因是不想一辈子给别人打工看不到头，况且年龄越来越大就很害怕失业，所以想自己创业搞点项目！目前还没有特别好的项目，即便没有好的项目我也选择了先离职原因就是上家单位加班多熬夜多身体受不了！目前准备尝试的几个项目 1 、抖音电商 2 、抖音自媒体(美食方向) 为此特意注册了公司用于项目运作所需！但是现在有点迷茫不知道何去何从！有时候想不如继续找份工作上班算了，如果重新找份工作或许没有之前工作那么累，而且过的也算滋润吧，但是回头再想想一眼看不到头的打工生活我就够了！反正现在就是有点迷茫有点徘徊！","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796531","replies":34,"created_ts":1629264772,"created":"13:32:52","title":"92 年运维辞职创业给点建议","author":"yitiaoxiaoxi","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yitiaoxiaoxi","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5f0c733632a70f3e5667ce5b6b7859af?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796628,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629371484","description":"<p>事情是这样的：我在 Monash 的 Information Technology 念 Master，我们 Java 课让我们做一个 CLI 的猜数字小游戏。我做了之后给 tutor 发了源码，tutor 的第一句话是「 Too many Java coding standard violations 」。</p>\n<p>我想了半天，我代码除了没按照 BlueJ 的 class template 来写之外，好像没有别的「违反标准」的行为吧……</p>\n<p><img alt=\"BlueJ 的默认 class 模板\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/08/18/G5TrkDMo1dXBAuv.png\"/></p>\n<p>我的代码风格如下（应该能说明一些问题？）：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"截屏 2021-08-18 21.05.48.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/08/18/GZi8ITa6nUAHbSr.png\"/></p>\n<p>其实我也不太确定是不是真的有「违反标准」，就来 V2EX 问问各位「真正的」 Java 程序员，平时写代码是不是严格使用「制表键来缩进」等等这类比较「呆板」（我找不到一个中性的形容词，总之就是这么个意思吧？）的标准……</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796628","replies":31,"created_ts":1629292554,"created":"21:15:54","title":"该如何理解「 Java Coding Standard」？","author":"Astrian","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Astrian","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/622f46cf617d609478f381cd9259559e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":796602,"node":"全球工单系统","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/gts","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_mini.png?m=1591791660","description":"<p><img alt=\"b29631e9c2fba2efe9188bba37ab232.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/001Y8Mztgy1gtl324an1qj60wi1yc4ph02.jpg\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796602","replies":30,"created_ts":1629279956,"created":"17:45:56","title":"京东让我允许追踪\r\n要不要脸啊","author":"sekisui","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/sekisui","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da1d/77d2/522522_mini.png?m=1607228287"},{"id":796601,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533","description":"<p>虽然 IE 时期还要兼容不同的浏览器平台差异，但是好歹有 ECMAScript 标准在那放着，也都遵循 HTML+CSS+JS 的原则。\n现在可好，每家小程序平台就像是一个有着自主规则的浏览器，通过独特的语言特性来做技术壁垒，你要想做开发一款多平台都能用的小程序要么写多套，要么用跨端方案。作为开发者真是日了狗了，开发体验为 0，为负数！</p>\n<p>你想想，要是你开发了一款网站，结果只能谷歌浏览器上浏览，而不能其他浏览器上浏览，这是什么感觉。</p>\n<p>我不否认小程序是一个很伟大的跨端方案，可是为啥不去共同建立一个生态，反而是窝里斗呢。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/796601","replies":25,"created_ts":1629279684,"created":"17:41:24","title":"开发小程序比兼容 IE 还烦躁","author":"Elephant696","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Elephant696","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ed3/e5b7/268036_mini.png?m=1514534938"}]